				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks, Docinatrix! I had a lot of fun writing this one. As to the end bit, I think that part of what could be making it feel a bit clichéd is that the last sentence is slightly on the melodramatic side. </p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

