					<p>This story made me cold just reading it. I agree with the general consensus within the comments that the story sustains a wonderful feel of detachment which, I imagine, mirrors Troy&#8217;s feelings (or lack there of) throughout the story.</p>
<p>For this reason it reminded me of the Dexter books. Which, I hasten to add, is a good thing.</p>
