				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>This is ace! Cold, clinical, medical, detached and very creepy. Great writing.<br />
I felt close to the action. Reading it induced a mild claustrophobic kind of feeling.<br />
Despite that I really enjoyed the story :D.</p>
<p>+1 for consistency on the italics &#8211; the way they come out, <em>hyper</em> feels like a tall, skinny, pale reaper pointing at a dictionary definition, whereas <em>exsang</em> feels more like the cheery morgue attendant munching on his burger while showing you the body. Iyswim&#8230; (-_-)</p>
<p>Yay!</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

